The board and staff of the Nigeria Football Federation will tomorrow, Friday hold a solemn assembly to seek the face of God as a new dawn begins at the Glasshouse,National Daily learnt.
The solemn assembly which will hold by 9am before the staff begin the day’s business is designed to rededicate the Federation before God.
According to the President, the new NFF cannot do anything without God, and for everyone we must look up to God to achieve anything.
 
